MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 27.25% to NT$7,771,780,000 from NT$10,682,861,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           7,771,780        10,682,861  
YOY%             -27.25%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           40,171,293       43,522,294  
YOY%              -7.70% 
=================================================================
 